READ BEFORE EDITING:
1. Read AGENTS.md
2. Read AI-EDIT-PRECHECK.md
3. Read the target file before changing it

MANDATORY:
- Do small targeted edits.
- Keep compatibility with existing source.
- Do not hardcode slug/path/category if data already exists.
- For clone/routing issues, check meta -> generated json -> render js -> href -> folder path.
- Add short comments only where the owner must edit by hand later.
- Keep code easy to read, easy to edit manually, easy to clone.
